attributeSource.infoString2: Coldwell Banker Residential Brokerage - Johns Creek/Duluth

data.description: Great home for a first time home buyer or investor looking for a buy and hold rental. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, split level, on over half an acre with a large fenced in back yard. Both bathrooms have upgraded Bluetooth speaker vent fan and lights, and his and her closets in the primary bedroom. The primary bathroom has been updated from the floor up including an extra deep soaking tub and the guest bathroom has a newer corner vanity. Eat in Kitchen with floating island, vaulted family room with a natural gas fireplace with vinyl flooring. All windows have been replaced with top of the line vinyl replacement windows. 2020 Samsung upgraded steam washer and dryer. Upgraded electric surge protector and a 12x20 Shed with 2 lofts is included on the property for storage. Bonus...an Electric Car Charger is included in the garage which would allow a 1 time tax break of around $4,500, SHOW ANYTIME, VACANT!!!
